OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782544686
OL,3,CWhen will the record-breaking UK
OL,4,Cheatwave end?
OL,6,FThe UK has seen extreme heat and
OL,7,Frecord-breaking temperatures this week.
OL,9,FBut the question everyone is now
OL,10,Fasking is - when is it going to cool
OL,11,Fdown?
OL,13,FFor those who don't like it hot, there
OL,14,Fis a little bit of a wait for the
OL,15,Ftemperatures to drop to a more
OL,16,Fcomfortable level.
OL,18,FITV News breaks down what the next few
OL,19,Fday will look like.
OL,21,FHow long is the heatwave going to stay?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
