OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782544686
OL,3,CWhen will the record-breaking UK
OL,4,Cheatwave end?
OL,6,FWe have seen four days of temperatures
OL,7,Fclose to, or above, 35C and Friday is
OL,8,Fno exception.
OL,10,FOver the weekend, the heat and high
OL,11,Ftemperatures will remain in many
OL,12,Fareas, though there is also a risk of
OL,13,Fthunderstorms due to the humid and
OL,14,Funstable air.
OL,16,FAn area of high pressure - called a
OL,17,F"heat dome" - has brought dangerously
OL,18,Fhot weather from France this week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
