FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782544686
OL,3,CWhen will the record-breaking UK
OL,4,Cheatwave end?
OL,6,FOn Saturday, that will continue to
OL,7,Fextend into the UK and parts of the
OL,8,Fsouth-east, bringing temperatures of
OL,9,F32C or more.
OL,11,FThe "heat dome" will then gradually
OL,12,Fsink away from northern England and
OL,13,Fparts of north Wales, and conditions
OL,14,Fwill be much more manageable with a
OL,15,Fmore typical British summer setup.
OL,17,FThere will be sunshine, and it will
OL,18,Ffeel very warm, but we will have a
OL,19,Fmild, stuffy night again in places.
OL,21,FSo, it's staying hot?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
