PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782544686
OL,3,CWhen will the record-breaking UK
OL,4,Cheatwave end?
OL,6,FIt will feel fresher on Sunday as the
OL,7,Fextreme heat of this week will give
OL,8,Fway to top temperatures nearer 26 and
OL,9,F27C.
OL,11,FThe sun is still at its maximum
OL,12,Fstrength at this point in the year, so
OL,13,Fit will remain very warm - but it will
OL,14,Fbe more comfortable and manageable
OL,15,Fwith less impact on health services
OL,16,Fand infrastructure.
OL,18,FOvernight, it will remain mild but not
OL,19,Fas restless or stuffy from Sunday
OL,20,Fonwards.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
